NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::CheckExtraTests - check xt tests before release

VERSION
    version 0.002

SYNOPSIS
    In your dist.ini:

       [CheckExtraTests]

DESCRIPTION
    Runs all xt tests before release. Dies if any fail. Sets
    RELEASE_TESTING, but not AUTHOR_TESTING.

SEE ALSO
    *   Dist::Zilla

AUTHOR
      David Golden <dagolden@cpan.org>

